{"tid":2370951,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"A24版《The Last of Us》  Casey Affleck再演沉鬱中佬","createTime":"2021-01-18T11:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T12:42:34.000Z","uid":250039,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbb5a738eca76cdaa5e0eda77d257f01634f5f9","tid":2370951,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T11:50:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CKL1yFWnoTW/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCKL1yFWnoTW%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=5357b0a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCKL1yFWnoTW%2F&h=83aee48b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CKL1yFWnoTW/</a><br />\n<strong>《生命之光》(Light of My Life)<br />\nA24版The Last of Us</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/138709200_2446813585613796_1516445267957953170_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=ta1POETK9swAX-1laSf&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=fb5c427ec23abd12c3532bf20da4a2c9&amp;oe=602CF2D8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F138709200_2446813585613796_1516445267957953170_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3Dta1POETK9swAX-1laSf%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dfb5c427ec23abd12c3532bf20da4a2c9%26oe%3D602CF2D8&h=da7b4afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年憑《情繫海邊之城》演出一位喪失家人，久久未能釋懷，心靈破碎的中年漢，細膩動人的演技，為他帶來奧斯卡最佳男主角的殊榮。演而優則導，作為Casey Affleck第二部執導的長片，2020年的《生命之光》(Light of My Life)言簡意賅的帶出一場名副其實愛的歷險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ltrbxd.com/resized/sm/upload/oi/p2/yl/ad/light-of-my-life-1200-1200-675-675-crop-000000.jpg?k=6dcbe48d11\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ltrbxd.com%2Fresized%2Fsm%2Fupload%2Foi%2Fp2%2Fyl%2Fad%2Flight-of-my-life-1200-1200-675-675-crop-000000.jpg%3Fk%3D6dcbe48d11&h=19a35091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為一場世紀瘟疫令全球女性大多死於非命，一位父親帶著女兒在末世中掙扎求存的設定上，不禁令人想起情節差不多的The Last of Us，雖然情節雷同，但劇本更著墨於描寫父親及女兒之間的羈絆。談及一切可能早已盪然無存的道德及倫理、逃生時的要訣、若父親死去該如何自處，末世之下父親向女兒叮嚀更是令人揪心。<br />\n<br />\n自編自導自演的Casey Affleck很清楚整齣電影的定位，低成本製作，但找來一位甚具靈氣11歲的Anna Pniowsky飾演女兒一角，為電影加上不少分數。不走商業片的套路，配合上冷風颯颯，鵝毛大雪，也能營造出一個冰冷冷的末世。電影的鏡頭亦落足心思，利用俯視角度拍攝的對話戲也是別開生面，令人不禁想起近年非常成功的獨立電影發行商A24。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PoHADU7Oe-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPoHADU7Oe-g&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=8a8e2adb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PoHADU7Oe-g</a><br />\n各位啱睇不妨俾個like，得閒睇完戲會打下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/movies234.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmovies234.hk&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=c8415589\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/movies234.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/movies234.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmovies234.hk&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=b05341be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/movies234.hk</a>"},{"pid":"00b1e6ce2c9842707528632c87049622244b4db9","tid":2370951,"uid":300687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"呢套戲都唔係a24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eac985a638908b2657a00281b9f9b77faaf468b","tid":2370951,"uid":250039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00b1e6ce2c9842707528632c87049622244b4db9","tid":2370951,"uid":300687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"呢套戲都唔係a24<img src=\"/assets/faces